import { Grid, Typography, Box } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'
import banner2 from '../images/banner2.jpg'
const Banner = () => {
  return (
    <Grid container sx={{background:`url(${banner2})`,height:'40vh',display:'flex', justifyContent:'center', alignItems:'center'}}>
       <Grid item sx={{}}>
         <Typography variant="h1" component="h1" sx={{ color: '#fff', WebkitTextStroke:'1px black'}}>
          Welcome to our website
               </Typography>
       </Grid>
    </Grid>
  )
}

export default Banner
